1. The user launches the app and taps the screen to begin activity.
2. In activity, the user controls the dot via tilt mechanism.
3. In activity, the user may tap the screen to reset dot.
4. In activity, the user may control the dot to the top of screen to display street address at bottom of screen.
5. In activity, the user may control the dot to the bottom of the screen, but must tilt the device nearly vertical to ensure it touches the bottom of screen.
6. In activity, the user may shake the device to clear activity. 